The appearance of the subsun can vary, but it often looks like a glowing patch of light mirroring the sun's position. It moves with your perspective because it's dependent on the alignment of the ice crystals relative to your viewing angle. This phenomenon is part of the broader family of halo effects, which includes sundogs, halos, and light pillars.

Subsun sightings are rare but beautiful, often adding a magical quality to high-altitude views!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gE52E3G</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LosPer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>In case you haven’t seen a diving piglet yet today</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RjJpddh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xZfMjP5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RjJpddh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[luvdechub]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dude has it right!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2A66jDH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7BPSSve.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2A66jDH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DumpingSh1tandBeingKind2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What a talkative kitty :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mM2uY7G</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kb5Dm4I.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source:  https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFQ-4ioJaBc/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mM2uY7G</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>99.9% of politicians, news broadcasters suddenly united and tried to portray him as a danger.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/U5PBhtP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NxI3GR8.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/U5PBhtP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Grogu007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is dog, who’s this?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VRJYJ1L</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x6wo3GK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto